Incoming livestream: of the day. The very last session of the con. I hope we have all learned a number of things, at least half of which will stick in our minds, the rest of it.


3
00:00:22.335 --> 00:00:37.015
Incoming livestream: Maybe we'll rewatch the talks again on YouTube. So we have two more talks, and then, you know, whatever festivities, we choose to close this thing out with. So my ask is that we…


4
00:00:37.275 --> 00:00:38.565
Incoming livestream: Lock in.


5
00:00:40.955 --> 00:00:43.615
Incoming livestream: Pay attention to the last couple speakers.


6
